{"tid":1884570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭藍田德田邨派口罩，會喺柯創盛(民建聯)定葉梓傑(民主黨)嘅選區派？","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T06:20:17.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed7572d5cb95ef4f1c6e253807fe43fc5f78526","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMHCeMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMHCeMT.jpg&h=72166631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>廣德 J17</strong><br />\n廣田邨、德田邨（德義樓、德樂樓、德欣樓、德康樓、德盛樓、德隆樓）及康盈苑<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯 ①. 柯創盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4,514 51.06% </span><br />\n人民力量 ②. 譚得志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4,327 48.94%<br />\n<br />\n<strong>興田 J18</strong><br />\n興田邨、康華苑及德田邨（德敬樓、德禮樓及德瑞樓）<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">民主黨 ①. 葉梓傑 4,751 58.17% </span><br />\n工聯會 ②. 余邵倫 3,417 41.83%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/17/P2020021700792_photo_1171407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F17%2FP2020021700792_photo_1171407.jpg&h=95d959e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥到藍田德田邨，聯同保良局派發口罩、食物、健康資訊單張及其他物資予幾位領取綜緩的獨居長者，並向他們送上問候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713a04d8090cfb2559821a7bdf73da04c49da520","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"保良局劉陳小寶長者地區中心<br />\n地址 九龍藍田德田邨藍田社區綜合大樓一樓及德欣樓地下B翼<br />\n<br />\nall J17<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b988eead1d5067e97d4cbda1e51c029a5c62534","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"觀塘區議會過去長期由親中派佔絕對多數，亦是最多親中共派區議員自動當選的區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Kwun_Tong_District_Council_%282019%29.svg/800px-Kwun_Tong_District_Council_%282019%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F8f%2FKwun_Tong_District_Council_%25282019%2529.svg%2F800px-Kwun_Tong_District_Council_%25282019%2529.svg.png&h=8c980e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC8Rdnu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC8Rdnu.png&h=8f56d65e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92d4673b9e063e8c87fb0bec2061663de996c2bb","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"check ip<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/MASK-CLEANER-200217-2330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FMASK-CLEANER-200217-2330.jpg&h=bb4e7cda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee0ae06b39876d623666b7c561f3db26667ddb1c","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"譚得志說，結果與預期差不多，雙方票數接近，認為自己落敗原因在於落區不夠早和不夠密。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-09-07 <br />\n人民力量副主席譚得志則表示，擬派出六至七人參與明年區選，集中於九龍東和新界東，自己會則揀選建制派自動當選的選區參選，其中狙擊民建聯立法會議員柯創盛亦是選項之一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbb18a4577f59ff932c9f65204072ff2786c125","tid":1884570,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0ae06b39876d623666b7c561f3db26667ddb1c","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"譚得志說，結果與預期差不多，雙方票數接近，認為自己落敗原因在於落區不夠早和不夠密。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-09-07 <br />\n人民力量副主席譚得志則表示，擬派出六至七人參與明年區選，集中於九龍東和新界東，自己會則揀選建制派自動當選的選區參選，其中狙擊民建聯立法會議員柯創盛亦是選項之一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"好唔抵"},{"pid":"18e46b73ed39e2ffa443aa70bd759b9206710d2f","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"譚得志在完成點票後承認落敗，認為自己敗於宣傳策略，因僅於藍田港鐵站擺街站，未有到「邨口」與街坊接觸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n約在兩小時的街站中，大多是「快必」自說自話，但途人多是匆匆而過，甚少對其望一眼。眼見街站冷淡，「快必」急忙開始消費最近的修例風波，亦不停提醒該區過往都是「冇得揀」，但今屆大家終於可以「有票投」，但街坊依然沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n最後，「快必」忍不住攻擊同區候選人，企圖通過大肆抹黑對手的卑污手段去撈取選票。譚還不斷強調在2016年參加立法會選舉時自己亦曾在同一個場地罷街站，但換來的是街坊一臉茫然，無人記得起有這回事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fa1e0a5d796c1f797eac97cab29baf97414b33","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbbb18a4577f59ff932c9f65204072ff2786c125","tid":1884570,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0ae06b39876d623666b7c561f3db26667ddb1c","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"譚得志說，結果與預期差不多，雙方票數接近，認為自己落敗原因在於落區不夠早和不夠密。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-09-07 <br />\n人民力量副主席譚得志則表示，擬派出六至七人參與明年區選，集中於九龍東和新界東，自己會則揀選建制派自動當選的選區參選，其中狙擊民建聯立法會議員柯創盛亦是選項之一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"好唔抵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"譚被指「空降」廣德選區，但他則認為自己並非空降，因為自上屆立法會選舉以來，自己在九龍東的街站從未停止，只是多數設立在港鐵站或街市外等遠離核心屋苑範圍的位置，才令選民形成錯覺。"},{"pid":"9462c2cc03366659375c198e8b09037324d56487","tid":1884570,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e46b73ed39e2ffa443aa70bd759b9206710d2f","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"譚得志在完成點票後承認落敗，認為自己敗於宣傳策略，因僅於藍田港鐵站擺街站，未有到「邨口」與街坊接觸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n約在兩小時的街站中，大多是「快必」自說自話，但途人多是匆匆而過，甚少對其望一眼。眼見街站冷淡，「快必」急忙開始消費最近的修例風波，亦不停提醒該區過往都是「冇得揀」，但今屆大家終於可以「有票投」，但街坊依然沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n最後，「快必」忍不住攻擊同區候選人，企圖通過大肆抹黑對手的卑污手段去撈取選票。譚還不斷強調在2016年參加立法會選舉時自己亦曾在同一個場地罷街站，但換來的是街坊一臉茫然，無人記得起有這回事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldMp55aOM1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DldMp55aOM1w&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=2533927f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldMp55aOM1w</a><br />\n譚得志屌票失敗, 爭小小票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢願意落區選已經好好架啦"},{"pid":"a68bda4183a9e4bba47e5f4eb03aa99f8b946f0d","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"藍田康田苑一家三口確診冠狀病毒，區內人人自危，不遠處平田邨住着秀珍、秀嫻、美香三個獨居長者，美香說：「唔到你驚唔驚，自己要小心。」三人不約而同將紙巾放在口罩內，除了剛才所說的小心，也延長口罩壽命。<br />\n<br />\n秀珍67歲年紀最輕，也最多主意，自創紙巾蘸酒精，再放入口罩，防毒、殺菌、耐用，一次過滿足三個願望。話說去年她動了白內障手術，買酒精洗刷雙眼，要不是捱了這一刀，如今也沒酒精用，她說：「我好在嗰時買到，仲喺嗰時買到。」她習慣要緊說話說兩次。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日藥用酒精也是稀世奇珍，她只剩下小半支，消耗酒精來延長口罩壽命，究竟這條數是否划算，恐怕數學家也說不上，她省着用，每次兩滴，對摺紙巾放入口罩，如此這般每次換紙巾，口罩則可用上五天，「紙巾放入（酒精）裏面消毒，除一次掉一次，除一次掉一次。」<br />\n<br />\n三人當中秀珍算是「富戶」，家中有大拿拿四、五個口罩，然而訪問當天面上口罩頗見風霜，起了毛頭，多次反覆使用畢竟留下歲月痕迹，她說：「落街就戴，落街就戴，唔落街就唔戴。」她說一旦口罩用光便不出戶，說得輕鬆平常，到底獨居，衣食住行閣下自理，不出戶不行，「起碼一日一次，起碼一日一次，落去買餸。」<br />\n<br />\n身旁的秀嫻年屆八十一，撐着枴杖走路，又有尿頻，南征北討狩獵口罩划不來，然而三朵金花之中她最多金句：「屎急尿急有三急，皇帝都唔阻得，又唔係多，放低二両咁就夠死，排緊隊唔知去邊度放。」幸而人民力量譚得志（快必）送口罩上門，解燃眉之急，如今她剩下兩個，乃鎮家之寶。<br />\n<br />\n建制區議員冇幫過<br />\n去年底區選快必在鄰區「廣德」敗給民建聯柯創盛，難得仍然有心，秀嫻透露：「點爭呀？柯仔平時同我哋開會：『老友記，舉起左手，舉埋右手，畀啲掌聲自己！』第二樣就係：『藍田老友記係我嘅心肝寶貝！』而家非常時期呀大佬，一個口罩都未派過！」<span style=\"color: red;\">柯創盛立足藍田，躋身立法會，疫情爆發後，三個心肝寶貝都沒見過這個人。</span><br />\n<br />\n84歲的美香<span style=\"color: red;\">剛從平田非建制區議員陳易舜手上接過酒精、口罩</span>，地區組織又派來三個，她嘆道：「歸根究柢好在社區照顧我哋長者，呢度畀啲嗰度畀啲，我哋勉強又慳啲，有啲希望啦！希望政府撥多啲出嚟，照顧多啲長者，我哋起碼唔使咁徬徨。」"},{"pid":"82a01b962a373c8b3bee3fb11bf52ab369df8405","tid":1884570,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9462c2cc03366659375c198e8b09037324d56487","tid":1884570,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18e46b73ed39e2ffa443aa70bd759b9206710d2f","tid":1884570,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"譚得志在完成點票後承認落敗，認為自己敗於宣傳策略，因僅於藍田港鐵站擺街站，未有到「邨口」與街坊接觸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n約在兩小時的街站中，大多是「快必」自說自話，但途人多是匆匆而過，甚少對其望一眼。眼見街站冷淡，「快必」急忙開始消費最近的修例風波，亦不停提醒該區過往都是「冇得揀」，但今屆大家終於可以「有票投」，但街坊依然沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n最後，「快必」忍不住攻擊同區候選人，企圖通過大肆抹黑對手的卑污手段去撈取選票。譚還不斷強調在2016年參加立法會選舉時自己亦曾在同一個場地罷街站，但換來的是街坊一臉茫然，無人記得起有這回事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldMp55aOM1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DldMp55aOM1w&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=2533927f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldMp55aOM1w</a><br />\n譚得志屌票失敗, 爭小小票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢願意落區選已經好好架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"講左N次快必比廢老打完先至忍唔住屌鬼"},{"pid":"67be2fa4c8f13147fbeff869ab264e84774621bd","tid":1884570,"uid":252985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"根本換走快必就就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class